# Design System

## Colors
- Primary: #2563eb (blue)
- Secondary: #7c3aed (purple)
- Success: #059669 (green)
- Warning: #d97706 (orange)
- Error: #dc2626 (red)

## Typography
- Heading: Inter Bold, 24px
- Body: Inter Regular, 16px
- Caption: Inter Regular, 14px


## Component Patterns
- Buttons: Rounded corners (8px), 44px height
- Input fields: Border radius 8px, 16px padding
- Cards: Shadow elevation 2, 12px radius

